end.description: Treat it as the last button and add a margin left margin to it.
end.description_zh: 视为最后一个按钮并为其添加左边距 margin 。

start.description: Treat the first button as having a margin with a right margin added to it.
start.description_zh: 视为第一个按钮并未其添加右边距 margin 。

tag.description: Specifies the custom tag to be used on the root element.
tag.description_zh: 指定在根元素上使用的自定义标签。
